SYSTEM

MAIN.TS - INITIALIZATION : BOOTS THE APP : LOADS TEXTURES, UI ELEMENTS 

STARFIELD.TS - VISUAL EFFECTS : THE BACKGROUND

SLOTMACHINE.TS - GAME CONTROLLER : CORE OF THE GAME : BETTING, SPINNING, ANIMATIONS, GAME STATE

REEL.TS - MANAGE ENTITY : COLUMN OF SLOT MACHINE : HANDLE SYMBOLS : DYNAMIC SCALING :

CONFIG.TS - CONFIGURATION OF THE GAME : PAYLINE MATRIX :DEFINE CONSTANT VALUES : ASSET AND UI ELEMENTS

CORE MECHANICS & GAME LOOP

SPINNING -  5 SYMBOLS IN AN ARRAY IN A REEL : GSAP TO TWEEN : RANDOM ASSIGN TEXTURE

BETTING - CAN TYPE OR + - : BLOCK WHEN SPINNING : AUTO SPIN STOPS WHEN NO BALANCE

WIN VALID - GSAP COMPLETES ACIVATE REELSCOMPLETE() : COUNT SCATTER : LOOPS THROUGH PAYLINES ARRAY : EVALUATES WILD SYMBOL FROM L TO R : 

FEEDBACK - WIINING SYKMBOLS HIGHLIGHTED : SAP SCALES IT 


DEV 
MASKING - FOR BETTER UI

RESOLUTION - HANDLERESIZE() USE VIEPORT DIMENTIONS : RESPONSIVE

Grid: 5 Reels Ã— 3 Rows
Paylines: 5 Fixed Lines
-------------------------------
Symbol Composition: 

5 Low Symbols 
3 High Symbols 
1 Wild 
1 Scatter 

----------------------------------
Payouts are calculated based on the Total Bet.

1. Base Wins (3-of-a-Kind)

        Symbol Tier     	        Base Multiplier (3 Matches)
    LOW (Planets, Rocks)	              0.5x Total Bet
    HIGH (Stars, Galaxy)	              2.0x Total Bet
    WILD (Substitute)	                 10.0x Total Bet
-----------------------------------

2. Length Multipliers (The "Big Win" Logic)

        Match Length                        Multiplier
        3 Symbols                    1x (Standard Base Win)
        4 Symbols                    5x (Big Win)
        5 Symbols                    20x (Mega Win)
-----------------------------------

3. Total Win Table (Calculated)

    Symbol      3 Matches (Common)          4 Matches (Uncommon)            5 Matches (Rare)
    LOW             0.5x                           2.5x                           10x
    HIGH            2.0x                           10x                            40x
    WILD            10x                            50x                      2,000x (JACKPOT)
-----------------------------------

Jackpot

The standard math is overridden if the player lands 5 Wilds on a valid payline.

Trigger: 5 Consecutive Wilds.
Payout: 2,000x Total Bet.
-----------------------------------

Scatter Free Spins

Scatters pay in any position (they do not need to be on a payline line).

Requirement: Land 3 or more Scatters anywhere on the screen.

Reward: 10 Free Spins.

Rules: Free spins are played automatically at the triggering bet amount but do not deduct from the balance.

          Scatter Count                      Reward                  Math
            3 Scatters                   10 Free Spins           Base Reward
            4 Scatters                   15 Free Spins           Base + 5 Extra
            5 Scatters                   20 Free Spins           Base + 10 Extra